# Title: Credentials In Files - Linux
# Author: Igor Fits, oscd.community
# Date: 2020-10-15
# Level: high
# Description: Detecting attempts to extract passwords with grep
# MITRE Tactic: Credential Access
# Tags: attack.credential-access, attack.t1552.001
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/linux/auditd/execve/lnx_auditd_find_cred_in_files.yml

type="EXECVE" "grep" "password"